        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nHi Patrick, I forgot that formatting will cause commits grow big, sorry about that.\n\nI think I should add some comments about changes.\n\nExtraction of some code to separate classes seems to be crucial to allow understand code and then write tests.\n\nI also think about making immutable wrappers for property/context/hash maps where it makes sense to prevent accidental changes and also as hint for other devs to not try edit them.\n\nAbout code changes, I wrote tests before refactoring original code so things should work as expected. No any guarantees however.",
